CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 22, 1941, pg. 10 reads: "Terrace Village Club Has Clever Fashion Show - Terrace Village Sewing and Charity Club sponsored a fashion show last Friday. The participants were popular young women and lovely children of the community...little Andrea Jean Shephard shows what the well dressed very young will wear...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Andrea Jean Shephard wearing light colored short sleeved dress, light colored bow in hair, and light colored shoes and socks, posed holding flowers, in Terrace Village for fashion show
